<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('partials/head', { title: 'ModBot — Advanced Discord Moderation' }) %></head>
<body>
  <div class="topnav">
    <div class="brand"><span class="dot"></span> ModBot Dashboard</div>
    <nav>
      <% if (user) { %>
        <a class="btn" href="/servers">My Servers</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/login">Login</a>
      <% } %>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>A super-advanced moderation bot,<br />with a full web console.</h1>
    <p>AutoMod, warnings, mod logs, welcome messages, reaction roles, custom commands, and a live embed builder — all configurable from this dashboard. Currently serving <strong><%= guildCount %></strong> server<%= guildCount === 1 ? '' : 's' %> as <strong><%= botTag %></strong>.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="<%= inviteUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">➕ Invite to a server</a>
      <a class="btn" href="<%= user ? '/servers' : '/login' %>">🖥️ Open Dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🛡️</div><h3>AutoMod</h3><p>Anti-spam, anti-invite, banned words, caps filter, mass-mention protection.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🔨</div><h3>Moderation</h3><p>Ban, kick, timeout, warn, purge — from Discord or the dashboard.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">💬</div><h3>Custom Embeds</h3><p>Visual embed builder with a live Discord-style preview.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🎭</div><h3>Reaction Roles</h3><p>Self-assignable roles via emoji reactions.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">📜</div><h3>Full Logging</h3><p>Mod actions, message edits/deletes, joins &amp; leaves.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🖥️</div><h3>Live Console</h3><p>Real-time event stream straight from the bot process.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div id="toast-root"></div>
</body>
</html>
